## Step 3.4ï½œå†™ã€ä½ é¡¹ç›®ä¸­æœ€é‡è¦çš„ä¸€æ¡ SQLã€‘

```sql
CREATE TABLE ai_market_summary AS
SELECT
    country,
    industry,
    ai_tool,
    year,
    age_group,
    company_size,
    AVG(adoption_rate)       AS avg_adoption_rate,
    SUM(daily_active_users)  AS total_dau,
    COUNT(*)                 AS records_count
FROM ai_raw
GROUP BY
    country,
    industry,
    ai_tool,
    year,
    age_group,
    company_size;
```

